		<a href="https://twitter.com/share?url=covid-india.xyz&text=A%20very%20simple%20covid%20india%20tracker%20that%20loads%20fast%20on%20slow%20networks" class ='fab fa-twitter icon'></a></p>

	<p>contant: nanirevanth45@gmail.com, donate: revanthkumar@upi</p>
